<emphasis box="[136,311,1908,1929]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="147">Erysimum aureum</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Bieberstein, M." box="[317,544,1908,1930]" pageId="0" pageNumber="147" refId="ref1430" refString="Bieberstein, M. (1808) Flora Taurico-Caucasica, vol. 2. Charkouiae, 478 pp." type="book" year="1808">Bieberstein (1808: 117)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
was first described by M. Bieberstein from the forests along the Terek River, between Mozdok and Kizlyar in 1808 (
<bibRefCitation author="Bieberstein, M." box="[392,561,1944,1966]" pageId="0" pageNumber="147" refId="ref1430" refString="Bieberstein, M. (1808) Flora Taurico-Caucasica, vol. 2. Charkouiae, 478 pp." type="book" year="1808">Bieberstein 1808</bibRefCitation>
