<emphasis box="[577,676,1944,1965]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="147">E. aureum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was first found in 
<collectingCountry box="[855,923,1944,1966]" name="Turkey" pageId="0" pageNumber="147">Turkey</collectingCountry>
